  "title": "Beautician",
  "description": "<p>Beautician (Full-Time) 美容师（全职）</p><p>📍 Location: Clementi Mall</p><p>📍 地点： 金文泰商场</p><p>💰 Salary Range: Basic $2,500 – $4,500 | Gross $3,000 – $6,000+</p><p>💰 薪资范围： 底薪 $2,500 – $4,500，总薪可达 $3,000 – $6,000+</p><p><br /></p><p>Your Key Responsibilities 你的主要职责</p><p>Deliver professional treatments: facials, skincare, IPL and other non-invasive therapies</p><p>提供专业疗程：脸部护理、护肤、IPL 及其他非侵入式项目</p><p><br /></p><p>Perform thorough skin analyses and craft personalized treatment plans</p><p>执行皮肤分析，为顾客量身定制疗程方案</p><p><br /></p><p>Foster strong client relationships to ensure repeat visits and referrals</p><p>维护客户关系，提升回头率及口碑推荐</p><p><br /></p><p>Maintain impeccable hygiene of treatment rooms and instruments</p><p>保持工作区与工具 清洁卫生，符合卫生标准</p><p><br /></p><p>Stay ahead of trends by constantly updating your skills and product knowledge</p><p>紧跟美容潮流，持续进修新技术与产品资讯</p><p><br /></p><p>What We’re Looking For 我们希望你具备</p><p>Minimum 2 years’ hands-on experience in beauty/facial treatments</p><p>至少 2 年 美容／脸部护理实战经验</p><p><br /></p><p>Bilingual proficiency in English & Mandarin</p><p>中英文双语沟通能力，能服务华语及英语客户</p><p><br /></p><p>A genuine passion for skincare and customer delight</p><p>热爱护肤行业，以客户满意为首要</p><p><br /></p><p>Detail-oriented, reliable, and a true team player</p><p>细心负责，具有团队合作精神</p><p><br /></p><p>Eager to learn and grow alongside Koiskin</p><p>渴望学习，与公司共同成长</p><p><br /></p><p>What You’ll Get 薪资与福利</p><p>Stable basic salary plus unlimited commission potential</p><p>稳定底薪 + 弹性提成，收入上不封顶</p><p><br /></p><p>Staff treatment perks and product discounts</p><p>员工护肤福利 + 产品优惠</p><p><br /></p><p>Regular training & clear career advancement path</p><p>定期培训 + 晋升机制</p><p><br /></p><p>Prime location inside Clementi Mall, just minutes from Clementi MRT</p><p>黄金地段，位于金文泰商场内，近金文泰地铁站</p><p><br /></p><p>Ready to Glow with Koiskin? 加入我们</p><p>📞 WhatsApp: +65 9858 0286</p>",
